=== 反修例期間遭到破壞 ===
[[File:Kowloon_Tong_Station_damage_20191006.jpg|缩略图]]
2019年10月6日，車站玻璃遭到反修例示威者的破壞，鐵閘和升降機遭到硬物打壞，噴漆塗污和開消防喉射水，並有人投擲雜物到東鐵綫路軌上。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1606957/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%A1%98%E7%AB%99%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%89%93%E7%88%86%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E5%A1%97%E9%B4%89-%E9%96%8B%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E5%96%89%E5%B0%84%E6%B0%B4|title=【修例風波】九龍塘站蒙面示威者打爆玻璃塗鴉 開消防喉射水|publisher=頭條日報|date=2019-10-06|accessdate=2020-02-03|archive-date=2021-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210921005500/https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1606957/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%A1%98%E7%AB%99%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%89%93%E7%88%86%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E5%A1%97%E9%B4%89-%E9%96%8B%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E5%96%89%E5%B0%84%E6%B0%B4|dead-url=no}}</ref>11月12日，九龍塘站車站設施再遭破壞，東鐵綫路軌遭到縱火，月台控制室的物品亦被燒至燻黑。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/397626/11-12-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%9C%E9%97%96%E5%85%A5%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%AB%99-%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%A1%98%E7%AB%99%E8%B7%AF%E8%BB%8C%E8%A2%AB%E7%87%92%E8%87%B3%E7%87%BB%E9%BB%91|title=【11.12】示威者深夜闖入港鐵站　九龍塘站路軌被燒至燻黑|publisher=香港01|date=2019-11-13|accessdate=2020-02-02|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323124101/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/397626/11-12-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%9C%E9%97%96%E5%85%A5%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%AB%99-%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%A1%98%E7%AB%99%E8%B7%AF%E8%BB%8C%E8%A2%AB%E7%87%92%E8%87%B3%E7%87%BB%E9%BB%91|dead-url=no}}</ref>

